mission:
  oneliner: |
    The groundbreaking frontend PaaS for business and enterprise applications
  usp:
  - Advanced browser capabilities — The current web at its heart is a platform for content, not applications. Qworum upgrades the web for better application support.
  - Real-time integration — Qworum is the world's first UI-level application integration technology. Contrary to iPaaS data integration solutions, with Qworum end-users will always see current, real-time data, not stale data.
  - Modular user interfaces — Qworum improves developer productivity and solves the "UI-monolith" problem for microservices architectures.
  - The world's first API technology for interactive processes. The world's first distributed web application technology.

downloads:
