  description: >
    30-second demo showing an e-shop that uses a remote shopping cart.
    The e-shop and the shopping cart are two different Qworum APIs hosted on different DNS domains.
    <a target="_blank" href='https://www.infoq.com/articles/qworum-modular-ui-architecture/'>This InfoQ article</a> describes in detail how this works.
    Note that consumer SaaS is currently not the main use case for Qworum.
